Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明是我的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該和我一樣 是這家神社的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該使用御神刀去打敗古物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我卻全然不知母親的名諱和樣貌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等 終至…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 非也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然 依舊令人愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時候到矣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十話 一夜之秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:05:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可隨欲而動 實可憐也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝亦如是哉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由既失 然亦有口腹之慾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝亦近獵食之時哉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然 汝近日之餌料 盡為下作之物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且無以履約也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如汝所知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已忘卻己所知乎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實乃愚者也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎聽到了什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹中飢渴也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論好食與否 但欲食之也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人之子 因何而怒也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝亦有噬食之需哉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚於此者 非吾輩之所能食也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究其因果 汝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 得決定是什麼獎勵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能守約直至最後的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該送你什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如若你不能做到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又該拿走什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦吧 違約之人 牽線之偶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅詢唯芳先生即可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的…真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 更衣小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭不痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 喝了咖啡好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子不餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許餓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 Guimauve的原料是紅色的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和裡面摻的東西有關
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得這個顏色對小夜再合適不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜應該喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅的顏色和這個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說 喝過咖啡舒服一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後問她想吃些什麼 她說Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肚子也餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃過飯得做準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把神社裡打掃得乾乾淨淨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的臉色…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒留個便條
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼穿著制服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不穿的話不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於現在的小夜來說也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是學生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能大意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杯子什麼的弄破的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 已經搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒鳥老師 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 更衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜也吃些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吃Guimauve不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 還有咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師喝點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不要咖啡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要杯紅茶吧 不加糖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 更衣同學的神社裡有不少貴重書籍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.96,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊的文獻之類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倉庫裡面的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能不能參觀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這得問一下父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會兒出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想最好今天去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 今天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 我不把裡面的東西帶出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且會很小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看一看 好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從以前就對古代傳奇和神話感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總沒有機會去看實物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這個鎮上 也是因為想看到實物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 更衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你為難了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我回頭再跟父親講吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒回來啊 你父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:19:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 到底是去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傳說和之前在課堂上講的鬼故事很像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為古物命名的是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然無論在哪本書中都沒有記載
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 正如它的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是個自古以來就吃人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且能打敗它的唯一物品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能打敗它的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御神刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 對不起發了會兒呆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這愚蠢的遊戲打算持續到什麼時候　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這本書 沒注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這紙…是新的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記載著傳說的應該是舊書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的全是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.50,0:21:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 全是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧寧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寧寧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這出鬧劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜 知道更衣的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.30,0:23:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂「更衣」就是「更換衣服」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常適合你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 BL00D-C
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是誰